author: scottbw
msg: Refactored IPreference to extend the IPreference interface in the parser package, harmonizing accessor methods (getName vs getDkey, getValue vs getDValue etc). The JPA column names haven't changed however, so this won't affect any existing data. This touches quite a few classes, but is a trivial renaming change and shouldn't affect any functionality.
